Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.49,0:00:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zanpakuto…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.45,0:00:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their shape and abilities are\Nbased on their Soul Reaper's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers gain power
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by learning their names\Nand synergizing with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.97,0:00:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are born with Soul Reapers\Nand die with Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.88,0:00:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what Zanpakuto are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.95,0:02:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This guy…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ordinary means won't\Nwork against him…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.61,0:02:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not here to play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have true power,\Nhurry up and show it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like fun…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell are they\Nup to inside me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destruction of our Zanpakuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:02:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if our Zanpakuto breaks,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it returns to normal along\Nwith our recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, however, our Zanpakuto\Nhave abandoned our bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and operate as separate entities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may be jumping to\Nconclusions if we believe that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these Zanpakuto are\Nno different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying that our killing\Nthese Zanpakuto manifestations
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the same as killing\Nour Zanpakuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose that is possible…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I think that's\Njumping to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we must ultimately\Nconfront the Zanpakuto,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can we fight rationally?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too easy, Renji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I thought he'd be\Nmuch better than that, Monkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not belittle him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have him\Ngiving up so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! He's up! He stood up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imbecile! Stop getting excited\Nover something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.03,0:04:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww! You don't have to hit me,\Nyou big ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it! You perverted brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't quibble like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't I your opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand anything,\Ndo you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time\Nfor weaklings like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, you did!\NThe big-assed broad said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said to stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep calling me names\Nlike weakling and whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what does that\Nhave to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is our true instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just what the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want to be weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We do not wish to be weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,\Nwe want to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're fed up with your weakness\Nand wish to leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure put it bluntly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Zabimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you intend to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renji?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So running away is\Nall that's left for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn! He anticipates nearly\Nevery move I make.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it wise to rest leisurely\Nin a spot like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You disappear from\Nmy range of vision
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to attack with\Nprojectile weapons…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're as rotten as you look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rotten? What of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it have anything to do\Nwith life and death?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not compatible\Nwith my way of fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a Zanpakuto whose\Nsole aim is to take lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in\Nhow my master fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought that\Nthe relationship between
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a Zanpakuto and a Soul Reaper
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was one of communication and synergy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about\Nother Zanpakuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm me. I cut down lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that was our sole\Nagreement between you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Then it's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you die and my Zanpakuto\Ndisappears, so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the feeling is mutual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This speed…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This power…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels as though\Nit's been a while
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since I unleashed my power\Nwithout holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And his raw nature…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:09:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's…on the offensive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out, Zanpakuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know there's more to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised…that I'm being\Npressured to this extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.73,0:09:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Ichigo Kurosaki released\Nhimself from Zangetsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you could run free inside him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the reason for
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki's strange\Ntransformation at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I say you're right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just that if that was the trick,\Nit wasn't worth my effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The relationship between\Na Zanpakuto and a Soul Reaper
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is communication and synergy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I know now that\Nthere are exceptions like you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who are kept reined in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I let you talk and\Nyou put me down like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been keeping me reined in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, why are you so\Ninterested in Ichigo…in us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your aim?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will know in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're up to,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.11,0:10:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I won't let you have your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll devour Ichigo and then\Ntake control of this body!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my true instinct!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you intend\Nto stand in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will extinguish you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice try!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weakling, coward…\NYou sure like to call people names!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you are a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other\Ndescription for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:12:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh… I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get more serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after all we've done to him,\Nhe won't get serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fun at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know everything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the time you gave up\Nsomething very dear to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.17,0:12:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that you tried\Ndesperately to get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And…that still, you don't\Nhave confidence in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we beat that precious girl to\Na bloody pulp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and hold up her head,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will you get serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:13:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know.\NThe reason why you cannot kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you went and did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't the man\Nwe were seeking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it. Where do you think\Nyou're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You intend to continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're leaving,\Ndo so after you beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no will to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or did you think we didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:14:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fight us. You defeat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means…you would be\Ndestroying your own power, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot attack us\Nbecause you fear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I don't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have left our master already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would not be strange if,\Nlike Soul Reapers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,death awaits us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renji…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot destroy your Zanpakuto\Nwith your own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you cannot\Ncome to terms with erasing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how can you reproach me\Nfor calling you weak?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ability to fight is not\Nthe only criteria for strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?\NIs that all you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you can get me\Nwith your low level of speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest assured. I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you have\Nup your sleeve, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My body…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?\NIs that all you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Shut up…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like what\Nhappened to me…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that his?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are just a Hollow.\NNot a power that I seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you can disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The pain…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What am I gonna do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I weak?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I hopeless, after all?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.09,0:16:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}– Just what have I been doing?\N– Say something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been forsaken\Nby my own Zanpakuto…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What have I been\Ndoing all this time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It hurts…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This pain… It hurts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's not my body that's\Nbeing hit that hurts…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's my life force.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.09,0:17:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey… What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine… Finish him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I still just…me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I said I was going to\Nbecome strong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But did I just fight blindly\Nand rush forward senselessly?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:18:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ichigo…said he fights\Nin order to protect.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is that his strength?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do I have? \NAnd why do I fight?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you have\Nyour way any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He escaped my spell\Nin such a short time…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.33,0:18:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just who is this man?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're protecting me?\NWhat's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just being me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.42,0:18:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're a part of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go spouting out\Nnice words again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Old Man Zangetsu is gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what\Nyou plan to do to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't know what\NI want to do with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's one thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so irritating.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a strange scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, protecting a Hollow's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, he may have\Nbeen a Hollow once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's a part of me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I do with him is my business\Nand I'm fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't intend to let\Na perfect stranger have his way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki, just what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your speech and conduct
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surely are not those of\Na Soul Reaper towards a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is Muramasa, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're wrong\Nabout one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've said it many times,\Nbut I'm not a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm human!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You intend to thrust me out\Nwith your own will?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki… You are\Nan interesting fellow indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be right that I'm weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.30,0:20:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have time to\Nramble on about such rubbish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:20:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rubbish?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take myself back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to do that is to\Nget Old Man Zangetsu back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it means destroying him…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone\NI must win against.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I have to become strong,\Nwhatever the cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two made me remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is how I truly feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to do that,\Nwhatever happens…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.75,0:21:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– I cannot lose!\N– I cannot lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.00,0:21:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Zabimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.71,0:23:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said to "Roar, Zabimaru."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.51,0:23:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so I roared.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.29,0:23:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I roar again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.28,0:23:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.11,0:23:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quincy Encyclopedia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.38,0:23:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My kids are cute too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.21,0:23:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? See? See?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.30,0:23:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get jealous
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.29,0:23:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just because he's at that\Nrebellious adolescent stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.74,0:23:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although,\Nmy girls aren't rebellious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.94,0:23:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all your son's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.53,0:24:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't pay attention to my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.12,0:24:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.94,0:24:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Parents are responsible\Nfor their child's actions!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.79,0:24:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,